column3: “Burned two bowls of this fruity light smoke this afternoon with a couple other club members. The dense buds made it around the circle a good 3 to 4 times, per bowl, before having to ash. Kept the awsome flavor right down till it was ash. Never harsh. The Euphoric feeling as well as the blabber mouth that incured started all most immediately. Everyone was talking intelligently laughing and having a good time. We then ...”
“very euphoric, i actually couldnt sleep after smoking this strain”

“extremely pungent smell but it's a very light-feeling high -- pretty relaxing but still able to be active and awake. I'd love this on a beach under the sun with some friends, or even just chilling in the house alone. the only thing I don't like about it is that it's such a light high, you don't realize you're getting high until you're there, but this is just preference.”
“HTF...so so, I have a headache and cotton mouth but I'm doodling pretty cool stuff and have the munchies. Not great benefits for me personally.”
“It taste great. Makes me talkative. But I get headaches everytime.”

“This is one of three strains that I received from Hawaïenne Outdoor Cannabis Grower from the land of SEVEN growing seasons compared with our only one growing season this Far North Montréal, Québec, and I am jealous of this fact alone.  The only garden that I have that would compare to his 7 growing seasons is up at our Chalet were have two Indoor Sun Lights which are arc lamps that truly represent  the light we recei...”

“Gets your mind soaring with a great tropical smell and taste with a hint of skunk under it. Good daytime strain. Long lasting too with a calming body buzz to go along with the more pronounced sativa effects.”
“shitty shitty bud i was very displeased my head hurt like a bitch afterwards”
